festival.introText: Europe's biggest indoor metal festival will host its 18th edition at BEC Arena, Manchester, on Saturday, November 4, 2023.

faqs.question: Accessibility information
faqs.answer: To contact Damnation for further information on accessibility and carer's tickets, please head to https://www.damnationfestival.co.uk/info.

faqs.question: How do I get to Damnation?
faqs.answer:
Directions:

Address – Bowlers Exhibition Centre, Longbridge Rd, Trafford Park, Stretford, Manchester M17 1SN

 

Nearest main rail station:

Piccadilly 

 

Nearest tram stop:

Parkway (Manchester Metrolink)

faqs.question: When is Damnation Festival?
faqs.answer: Damnation Festival is located at Bowlers Exhibition Centre across three stages.

faqs.question: Does Damnation Festival have any age restrictions?
faqs.answer: Damnation is a 14+ event. Those aged 14-17 must be accompanied by a person aged over 18 to gain admittance to the venue. Valid photo ID may be required.

news.title: Damnation festival announces first names for 2023 edition
